{"tid":1854832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國科學院初步發現雙黃連口服液可抑制新型冠狀病毒","createTime":"2020-01-31T17:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T14:57:48.000Z","uid":69678,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b4fab22f8645573438908fe6d56708c092358fe3","tid":1854832,"uid":69678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:00:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h3faxnx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh3faxnx.jpg&h=08363149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國科學院上海藥物所和武漢病毒所聯合研究初步發現，中成藥&quot;雙黃連口服液&quot;可抑制新型冠狀病毒。 目前這種口服液已在上海公共衛生臨床中心及同濟醫院開展臨床研究。<br />\n<br />\n雙黃連口服液由金銀花、黃芩及連翹組成。中醫認為，這三味中藥具有清熱解毒、表裡雙清的作用。現代醫學研究認為，雙黃連口服液具有抗病毒、抑菌、提高機體免疫功能的作用，是目前有效的抗病毒藥物之一。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1257711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D1257711&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=d47706d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1257711</a><br />\n<br />\n食完隻支那藥應該直接中毒死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76bb953c455c6576015f110d860eba288f1fc65","tid":1854832,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:02:17.000Z","msg":"緊急⚠️⚠️冇人知今日醫護有野搞！！<br />\n幫我入去十連！！<br />\n<br />\n「全城集氣撐醫護！！」今日三個行程終極懶人包！我要所有人出嚟集氣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1854740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1854740</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"447382f0d83a924d5d2ab7165ceb84149a49a3ff","tid":1854832,"uid":277186,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:03:00.000Z","msg":"等我仲買左50斤板藍根，原來係黃蓮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我今次破產都似"},{"pid":"1e7fbed9027d7c6ead0c877eeeda2e8cdc7fb907","tid":1854832,"uid":230391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cite